high_descs: Walk towards the counter
Grab a knife from the counter
Slice the bread on the counter
Walk with the knife towards the microwave
Put the knife in the microwave
Walk towards the  counter
Grab a slice of bread
Walk with the slice of bread towards the microwave
Put the slice of bread inside the microwave
Cook the slice of bread and take it out
Walk with the slice of bread towards the fridge
Put the bread slice inside the  fridge
anns.task_desc: Slice the bread, cook a slice in the microwave, put it in the fridge

high_descs: Turn around and walk toward the stove, then turn right to face the counter.
Take the silver knife on the counter.
Turn left and face the loaf of bread.
Slice the loaf of bread on the counter.
Turn left and walk to the microwave on the right.
Open the microwave door, put the knife inside, and close the door.
Turn right, then walk toward the toaster on the left.
Take a slice of bread from the loaf.
Turn left and walk back to the microwave on the right.
Open the microwave door, put the slice inside, close the door, and turn it on. Remove it when it's done and close the door.
Turn around and walk to the fridge.
Open the door, put the slice inside, and close the door.
anns.task_desc: Put a microwaved slice of bread in the fridge.
